TASKMAN 1.0

Objective : - To create a program that heavily implemented using design pattern
			- To get a job in Quora
			- (last but not least) To create a useful and cool program

Installation: - Python and wxPython (must install wxPython)

Description :
- TASKMAN is a program that created to manage all the user task easily
- in order to get started, just key in username and password. The program will create an account automatically if the username is not on the list
- in TASKMAN, user able to specify the priority, category and the deadline for each task created
- in additional, user also need to specify "milestone(s)" for every task they created
- the task is considered complete, if and only if, the user has completed all the milestone for the respective task
- the user able to specify the weight and details for every task milestone
- the user will be able to keep track the progress of their task based on the completed milestone

Features :
- Able to create a more concrete task, with it's milestone concept
- Able to customize the priority and category of the task
- Able to copy, remove, edit or sort the task with ease
- Able to track down the progress for each and every task
- TASKMAN will always keep all the info about the completed task from user
- Support multiple user in one machine, using simple username password authentication



